{"tid":626233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【豆腐渣？】廣州南沙橋下陷4cm 路面裂開封閉搶修","createTime":"2018-04-12T03:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T05:55:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"02cf8b3111044c7deb2ce62c06d247a16b7aa23f","tid":626233,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523492645_4337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523492645_4337.jpg&h=a9676274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地媒體報道，廣東廣州南沙區上橫瀝大橋往大崗方向的橋面，周三（11日）上午突然下陷4厘米，橋面裂開，有一包煙的寬度，須全線封閉搶修。<br />\n<br />\n事後，南沙區、市交委、交警、海事、市道路養護中心、廣東南沙港橋股份有限公司等有關部門到場視察，開展應急處理工作，包括採取雙向交通管制、應急檢測橋樑、在橋樑兩側安排專人駐守、保持24小時跟蹤監測等措施。<br />\n<br />\n當局指，前往廣州、市橋方向的車輛，可繞行南沙港快線或鳳凰大道；前往下橫瀝、中山、珠海方向的車輛，可繞行京珠高速或鳳凰大道。<br />\n<br />\n至於大橋恢復通行的具體時間仍有待確認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180412/58062722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062722&d=YbtR21lBoBPA9Rj5GNPUrgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1cead2e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062722&h=a212dc0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180412/58062722</a>"},{"pid":"a624539c0652c373b4b640e7350e57e6f06dfd14","tid":626233,"uid":14009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"自貿區 超英趕美<br />\n<br />\n大灣區 超越地球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7ec9941875e0968c6cc64e7542228498853322","tid":626233,"uid":38671,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"內地有內地做法，設計係咁，唔好因為一張相下判斷"},{"pid":"f4cf019246aec7b7ddc4f917e71142428ce8b100","tid":626233,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"唔成日維修工人邊有工開？冇工開點增加gdp?<br />\n大家說對不對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbeaeb30dd93ada2a536685c92d893040fc7cb3","tid":626233,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"原有設計黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3554464a10d51b421ec36a46b8537425eedfe40c","tid":626233,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"香港都就快一樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e356ecba9201ef2eedde4df135dbc3b586e81f3c","tid":626233,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"日常維修  不要過份炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47965b624c06c647bd8f8a823eebff74f5d261c0","tid":626233,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"施工圖係咁架屌你老母"},{"pid":"0b05c3348149529284c6da7edfbcc752c7913545","tid":626233,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"大6天橋都漂移，人工島可想而知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6658a55a7cb07be425876ed9781c7bc9a820a1b5","tid":626233,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac